: A Reappraisal of Normandy 1944</i></a>. <a href=\"/wiki/The_History_Press\" title=\"The History Press\">The History Press</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-75244-855-8\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-75244-855-8\">978-0-75244-855-8</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Death+in+the+Falaise+Gap%3A+A+Reappraisal+of+Normandy+1944&amp;rft.pub=The+History+Press&amp;rft.date=2011-03-01&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-75244-855-8&amp;rft.au=Jack+Livesey&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FDeath_in_the_Falaise_Gap.html%3Fid%3DBy-TkQEACAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJack+Livesey+%28impostor%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\">Jack Livesey, George Forty (16 September 2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books/about/The_Complete_Guide_to_Tanks_Armored_Figh.html?id=iKuduAAACAAJ\"><i>The Complete Guide to Tanks and Armoured Fighting Vehicles</i></a>. Southwater. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-78019-164-5\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1-78019-164-5\">978-1-78019-164-5</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Complete+Guide+to+Tanks+and+Armoured+Fighting+Vehicles&amp;rft.pub=Southwater&amp;rft.date=2012-09-16&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-78019-164-5&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FThe_Complete_Guide_to_Tanks_Armored_Figh.html%3Fid%3DiKuduAAACAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJack+Livesey+%28impostor%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></spa